Hey.
This map is a minigame where u have to climb.
If youre climbed up to the last block u have to surf a little rail.
In the middle of the map are 2 weapons : ak and m4
You can't go to the other spawn because under the platforms is a playerclip.
You can't pass through it.

PS: I made this map for fun :D


------------------------------------HF & GL-------------------------------------
